review: The clinic was very well maintained and all measures were taken during these covid times. Dr. Sumit was very patient and friendly and patiently answered all my questions. Would defenitely recommend it.

Doctors was really friendly, First ever dental check up it was so I was really worried but it went beyond my expectations , just loved the session. The faculty was also really good and friendly. Would recommend everyone to visit. Thanks

He is a very good human being i have witnessed till now in my life.Coming to my experience as a doctor's guidance it was like a big brother treating you.I would recommend everyone to kindly consult him for any help.

review: Dr. Sumit is very friendly and explained the issues very nicely. Had an immediate relief. Planning to visit him soon for the next step of treatment

Went here to get my root canal done. All hygiene measures during this covid time have been taken care of properly.. Dr. Sumit was very polite and patient throughout. Thoroughly satisfied with the service. Would definitely recommend divine dental Hub.

I recommend Dr. Sumit khatore 100%,  very friendly, polite and perfect at his work. Had an appointment for root canal, was very satisfied and happy after my appointment as it went with so much ease. ðŸ˜„

I have been there a couple of times due to my root canal and it is far much better than my experiences with the previous dentists. Would highly recommend Dr. Sumit Khatore for dental treatments.

Very satisfied with the dental treatment .
I would sincerely recommend other patients to visit the clinic ..
I visited for root canal treatment of my tooth followed by crown ..to my surprise it was rather painless..very happy with the work ..
